{"id":"frying-pan","term":"Frying-pan","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>(Heb. marhesheth, a “boiler”), a pot for boiling meat (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Leviticus 2:7\">Lev. 2:7</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Leviticus 7:9\">7:9</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Leviticus 2:7","Leviticus 7:9"]}